# KaixuSI — Implementation Directives
## The AI Brain Is Now Self-Hosted

**KaixuSI lives at:** https://kaixusi.skyesoverlondon.workers.dev  
**What KaixuSI is:** A Cloudflare Worker. This IS the brain. Not a proxy. Not Netlify. A self-hosted, always-on AI gateway that calls OpenAI / Anthropic / Gemini directly using YOUR keys.  
**Netlify's job:** Host the SuperIDE UI and backend functions. Netlify functions call KaixuSI — they do not call AI providers directly.  
**Auth:** `Authorization: Bearer KAIXUSI_SECRET` on every request (except `/health`)  
**Format:** JSON in, JSON out (or SSE for `/v1/stream`)

