## Authentication

Every authenticated request needs:
```
Authorization: Bearer KAIXUSI_SECRET
```

`KAIXUSI_SECRET` is:
- A Cloudflare Worker secret (set via `wrangler secret put KAIXUSI_SECRET`)
- A Netlify env var (same value — set in Site → Environment variables)

The Netlify functions read `KAIXUSI_SECRET` from their env and forward it to the worker. The IDE never exposes this token to the browser.

