## 14. Error Reference

| HTTP | When |
|------|------|
| 200 | Success |
| 401 | Missing or wrong `KAIXUSI_SECRET` |
| 400 | Bad request body / missing required fields |
| 404 | Unknown route |
| 500 | Worker misconfigured — check secrets are set |
| 502 | Upstream AI provider unreachable |

```js
